{"tid":2258561,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IZ*ONE宮脇咲良講日韓出道分別　坦言AKB48時期冇經驗都要上台","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T09:26:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1ecb2b0d82d006202cedd795e4920ba09ebfa791","tid":2258561,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"HKT48及AKB48出身的22歲宮脇咲良，現以IZ*ONE成員身份正在韓國工作，直至下年組合解散為止。早前宮脇咲良接受日本《ORICON NEWS》訪問時，分享她以韓團活動超過兩年的經驗，對比在日本活動7年以上的分別，坦言自己成長了不少，性格也變得更樂觀。<br />\n<br />\n宮脇咲良也在訪問中講到，兩年前要放下日本的工作及偶像身份，去到言語不通的韓國發展，讓她感到非常不習慣。此外加上韓國密集式的練習，宮脇咲良坦言一個人哭過不少之次，可是咬緊牙關又一一克服了。兩年多後的宮脇咲良講到終於覺得自己「正在努力」，可是仍感到不滿意，表示要讓粉絲看到她更大的進步。"},{"pid":"b2f06c604cd062218738ea44dbb43f9d783bb34f","tid":2258561,"uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201025/397104494506151936018374.jpeg/3XVnPYwZVlI4TssQyItJrHbCTsh4q67GmaWZLJmlmSw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201025%2F397104494506151936018374.jpeg%2F3XVnPYwZVlI4TssQyItJrHbCTsh4q67GmaWZLJmlmSw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8643daac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201025/397104497643622400296075.jpeg/eopvq5Tz5wyChmSxfX00Q2P49PNjHQuRmCFTxZghU8U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201025%2F397104497643622400296075.jpeg%2Feopvq5Tz5wyChmSxfX00Q2P49PNjHQuRmCFTxZghU8U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=eba750b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201025/397104500554600448654178.jpeg/iw3cbyyQKMUPC2iHHzE_Z9IYR6Cf_ST7-QfQ3PkH0Nw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201025%2F397104500554600448654178.jpeg%2Fiw3cbyyQKMUPC2iHHzE_Z9IYR6Cf_ST7-QfQ3PkH0Nw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2e272e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http